{"tid":1827303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［信報］民政事務專員動輒拉隊離場，因為得到張建宗許可","createTime":"2020-01-17T00:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-17T04:34:24.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ca90dae869f84bb03110246ff62614b5a4862827","tid":1827303,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T00:48:14.000Z","msg":"⋯⋯消息透露，一眾DO早前與張建宗會面，席間有人提出疑問，政府能下放多少權力予DO「拆彈」。<br />\n<br />\n不少DO擔心因臨場作出裁決遭外界責難，甚至遭到司法挑戰。當時有意見認為，若遇上爭議情況，最安全做法是拉隊離席，這樣做可避免作出裁決，即使民主派通過部分臨時動議，DO亦能撇清責任，此招獲張建宗認同。<br />\n<br />\n可撇清責任<br />\n<br />\nDO一般由資深政務官（AO）出任，通常每隔數年便調往其他部門。為了仕途着想，AO普遍不敢作出「出位」行為。政府中人估計，既然高層默許DO因應環境離席，其他區議會如出現民主派搞特別行動，相關DO料會緊跟隊形「快閃」撤離。⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2356184\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2356184&d=yrakYkBpMe8E3VCHF0kcyhURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=893cfc8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2356184</a>"},{"pid":"0f22ccab46f083e02a8fffdb4a3271251094f95d","tid":1827303,"uid":127988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T00:52:21.000Z","msg":"一國兩制存而不廢， 制度行之有效， 邊個搞法治over my dead body <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9969a21b2d75c0a8ca8121cc1e2a7dc3b3e2d01d","tid":1827303,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T00:55:59.000Z","msg":"根本就要reset成個香港制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重組政府架構"},{"pid":"78d56cd4950c88b3791fe9433c7e079fcc8e7845","tid":1827303,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T00:56:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">（新方向）文宣 x 包裝</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1826045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1826045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"223624465ced9d5fc84874d746dc1cef0a77e